Citation.sTitle: Isothermal and isobaric (vapour + liquid) equilibria of (alpha-pinene + n-butanol + n-octane)
Citation.sAbstract: The isothermal and isobaric (vapuor + liquid) equilibria for (alpha-pinene + n-butanol + n-octane) at the temperatures T = 353.15 K, and 363.15 K, and at the pressure p = 53.33 kPa, measured with an inclined ebulliometer are presented. The measured ternary results are analyzed and compared with those calculated from the UNIQUAC equation with temperature-dependent binary parameters obtained from the binary literature data. The results shown the UNIQUAC equation can be used to predict these ternary data.
